11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_NETEQ_TOOLS_PACKET_SOURCE_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_NETEQ_TOOLS_PACKET_SOURCE_H_
13
14#include <bitset>
15#include <memory>
16
17#include "modules/audio_coding/neteq/tools/packet.h"
18#include "rtc_base/constructor_magic.h"
19
20namespace webrtc {
21namespace test {
22
23// Interface class for an object delivering RTP packets to test applications.
24class PacketSource {
25 public:
26 PacketSource();
27 virtual ~PacketSource();
28
29 // Returns next packet. Returns nullptr if the source is depleted, or if an
30 // error occurred.
31 virtual std::unique_ptr<Packet> NextPacket() = 0;
32
33 virtual void FilterOutPayloadType(uint8_t payload_type);
34
35 protected:
36 std::bitset<128> filter_; // Payload type is 7 bits in the RFC.
37
38 private:
39 RTC_DISALLOW_COPY_AND_ASSIGN(PacketSource);
40};
41
42} // namespace test
43} // namespace webrtc
44#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_NETEQ_TOOLS_PACKET_SOURCE_H_
